{"word":"περιελαύνω","slug":"περιελαύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιελαύνω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ελῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to drive round</i>, <el>τὰς κύλικας π.</el> <i>to push</i> the cups <i>round</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to drive about, harass</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to draw</i> or <i>build round</i>, <el>περὶ δ' ἕρκος ἔλασσε</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>περὶ δ' ἕρκος ἐλήλαται</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>seemingly <a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἅρμα, ἵππον</el>), <i>to drive</i> or <i>ride round</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/></div>"}]}